{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14677,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/haram-to-curse-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":32176,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Forbidden to curse animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, during one of his journeys while a woman from the Ansar was on a camel. She disparaged it and cursed it. When the Prophet heard it, he said, \u201cUnload the camel and set\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/04\/not-sent-to-curse\/","url_meta":{"origin":32176,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: The Prophet not sent to invoke curses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Kariz ibn Samah reported: He was part of a delegation sent to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and it was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, pray against the tribe of \u2018Amir.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI was not sent to invoke curses.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 19\/189 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/do-not-curse-wind\/","url_meta":{"origin":32176,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Weather: Do not curse wind directed by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man cursed the wind in front of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cDo not curse the wind, for it only acts as it was commanded. Verily, whoever curses anything that does not deserve it, the curse will backfire against him.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32160,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/not-befitting-believers-curse\/","url_meta":{"origin":32176,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Not befitting believers to curse others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is not in the habit of cursing others.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2019 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0643\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0639\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064b\u0627 2019 \u0